.SH "SIGNALS"
.IX Header "SIGNALS"
On receipt of \fB\s-1SIGUSR1\s0\fR virtlockd will re\-\fIexec()\fR its binary, while
maintainin all current locks n' clients, n' you can put dat on yo' toast. This allows fo' live
upgradez of tha virtlockd service.
